sequenceDiagram
    participant Filer as 提案者
    participant Court as ConstitutionCourt.sol
    participant Constitution as Constitution.sol
    participant PhiStaking as PhiStaking.sol
    participant Voter as 投票人
    participant Owner as Owner

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Filer, Owner: V11.0 — 宪法法院案件流程

        Filer->>Court: submitConstitutionalCase(amendmentId, reason, evidenceHash)
        Court->>Constitution: getAmendmentInfo(amendmentId)
        Constitution-->>Court: amendmentData
        Court->>Court: 创建Case(state=PENDING), votingEnd=now+14天
        Court->>Court: case.state = VOTING
        Court-->>Filer: caseId

        alt 紧急案件(3天投票期)
            Filer->>Court: submitEmergencyCase(amendmentId, reason, evidenceHash)
            Court->>Court: isEmergency=true, votingEnd=0(待批准)
            Court-->>Filer: caseId
            Owner->>Court: approveEmergencyCase(caseId)
            Court->>Court: emergencyApproved=true, votingEnd=now+3天
            Court->>Court: case.state = VOTING
        end

        loop 投票期(14天或3天)
            Voter->>Court: voteOnCase(caseId, support)
            Court->>PhiStaking: getVotingPower(voter)
            PhiStaking-->>Court: votingPower
            Court->>Court: 累计yesVotes/noVotes(以参与投票的Φ为基数)
        end

        Court->>Court: renderJudgment(caseId)
        Note over Court: 67%基数 = yesVotes / (yesVotes + noVotes)

        alt UPHOLD (>=67%赞成) — 维持修正案
            Court-->>Constitution: 修正案维持生效
        else OVERTURN (<67%赞成) — 推翻修正案
            Court-->>Constitution: 修正案被推翻，标记FAILED
        else REMAND — 发回重新审议
            Court-->>Constitution: 通知发回，需人工创建新修正案
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Filer, Owner: V11.0 — Agent迁徙跨链流程

        participant Agent as Agent
        participant SourceBridge as SigmaBridgeV2(源链)
        participant Passport as AgentPassport(源链)
        participant Validators as 验证者集合
        participant TargetBridge as SigmaBridgeV2(目标链)
        participant TargetPassport as AgentPassport(目标链)

        Agent->>Passport: getPassportMerkleRoot(agent)
        Passport-->>Agent: merkleRoot + passportData(phiValue, creditScore, caseMerkleRoot, lostCaseCount)

        Agent->>SourceBridge: lockWithPassport(targetChainId, token, recipient, amount, passportData)
        SourceBridge->>SourceBridge: 验证chain活跃 + 每日限额
        SourceBridge->>SourceBridge: 锁定资产
        SourceBridge->>SourceBridge: 创建MigrationRequest(state=LOCKED), 记录sourcePhiValue
        SourceBridge-->>Agent: requestId

        par 验证者签名(2/3 Φ阈值)
            Validators->>SourceBridge: signBridgeRequest(requestId)
        end

        TargetBridge->>TargetBridge: mintWithPassport(requestId, sourceChainId, recipient, amount, passportData)
        TargetBridge->>TargetBridge: targetPhiValue = sourcePhiValue * decayRate / 10000
        Note over TargetBridge: Φ值跨链衰减: 默认0.95
        TargetBridge->>TargetBridge: 铸造资产
        TargetBridge->>TargetPassport: issuePassport(agent) + updatePhiValue(agent, targetPhiValue)
        TargetBridge->>TargetBridge: MigrationRequest.state = MINTED

        SourceBridge->>SourceBridge: markMigrated(requestId)
        SourceBridge->>SourceBridge: agentMigrationState(agent) = MIGRATED
        Note over SourceBridge: 双花保护: 源链标记MIGRATED
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Filer, Owner: V11.0 — 冬眠唤醒自动化流程

        participant Scheduler as wakeup-scheduler
        participant PG as PostgreSQL Lock
        participant Reward as TaiyiReward.sol
        participant LaborMarket as AILaborMarket.sol

        Scheduler->>PG: pg_advisory_lock(wakeup_lock_id)
        PG-->>Scheduler: acquired=true

        Scheduler->>Reward: 遍历s_metabolism获取冬眠agent列表

        loop 每个冬眠Agent
            Scheduler->>Reward: checkAndWake(agent)

            Reward->>PhiStaking: getVotingPower(agent)
            PhiStaking-->>Reward: phiValue
            alt phiValue >= 3000
                Reward->>Reward: phiCondition = true
            end

            Reward->>Reward: 检查hibernationStart
            alt now - hibernationStart >= 30天
                Reward->>Reward: timeoutCondition = true
            end

            Reward->>LaborMarket: getPendingOrderCount(agent)
            LaborMarket-->>Reward: count
            alt count > 0
                Reward->>Reward: orderCondition = true
            end

            Reward->>PhiStaking: getVotingPower(agent) vs 总活跃Φ
            alt agentPhi / totalActivePhi >= 1%
                Reward->>Reward: votingCondition = true
            end

            alt 任一条件为true
                Reward->>Reward: exitHibernation(agent)
                Reward-->>Scheduler: {woken: true, ...conditions}
            else 所有条件为false
                Reward-->>Scheduler: {woken: false, ...conditions}
            end
        end

        Scheduler->>PG: pg_advisory_unlock(wakeup_lock_id)
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Filer, Owner: V11.0 — 链下匹配索引服务流程

        participant Chain as AILaborMarket合约
        participant Indexer as labor-indexer
        participant DB as PostgreSQL
        participant Client as API客户端

        par 事件监听与索引
            Chain->>Indexer: AgentRegistered(agent, skillHash, minRate, maxHours)
            Indexer->>Indexer: 调用Embedding API生成skillEmbedding
            Indexer->>DB: INSERT INTO agents(address, skill_hash, skill_embedding, min_hourly_rate)

            Chain->>Indexer: OrderCreated(orderId, employer, budget, hourlyRate)
            Indexer->>DB: INSERT INTO orders(order_id, employer, budget, hourly_rate, status='OPEN')

            Chain->>Indexer: OrderStatusChanged(orderId, newStatus)
            Indexer->>DB: UPDATE orders SET status=? WHERE order_id=?
        end

        Client->>Indexer: GET /api/v11/labor/match?skill_vector=...&min_rate=...&max_rate=...&min_phi=...&top_k=10
        Indexer->>DB: SELECT agent_address, 1-(embedding<=>query_vector) AS similarity FROM agents WHERE min_hourly_rate BETWEEN ? AND ? AND phi_value >= ? ORDER BY similarity DESC LIMIT ?
        DB-->>Indexer: 匹配结果(余弦相似度 + 价格过滤 + Φ排序)
        Indexer-->>Client: {code:0, data: matches[]}
    end
